  "datePublished": "2026-04-07",
  "description": "The obligation on every office-holder to encode completed work so that future holders — or less capable agents — can perform it at lower cost. A general governance duty grounded in the settlement path: every discharge of a work duty should produce an artifact that moves the work one step toward process.",
  "name": "Duty of Progressive Encoding",
